-- ERG Swings to Second-Quarter Adjusted Net Income After Loss a Year Ago
-- Armorel Kenna
-- 2010-08-06T05:55:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-06/erg-swings-to-second-quarter-adjusted-net-income-after-loss-a-year-ago.html

          
          
             ERG SpA posted adjusted net income of
17 million euros in the second quarter, compared with a loss of
18 million euros in the year-earlier period.  
 ERG commented in a stock-exchange statement today.  
          
          


  


        